1999-09-29  Ken'ichi Handa  <handa@gnu.org>

	* ps-mule.el (ps-mule-font-info-database-ps): Typo fixed
	(normat->normal).  Use correct font names for Korean
	(Munhwa-Regular-KSC-EUC-H and Munhwa-Bold-KSC-EUC-H).

